 .gitignore for Terraform Projects

### Terraform ###
# Ignore local Terraform state files and plans
*.tfstate
*.tfstate.*
*.tfplan
plan.tfplan
plan.destroy.tfplan

# Ignore crash log files
crash.log
crash.*.log

# Ignore the .terraform directory, which contains providers and modules
.terraform/

# Ignore override files, as they are typically used for local testing
*.tfvars
*.tfvars.json
override.tf
override.tf.json
*_override.tf
*_override.tf.json

# Ignore CLI configuration files
.terraformrc
terraform.rc

### Operating System Files ###
# Ignore macOS-specific files
.DS_Store
.AppleDouble
.LSOverride

# Ignore Windows-specific files
Thumbs.db
ehthumbs.db
Desktop.ini

### IDE/Editor Directories ###
# Ignore common editor directories
.vscode/
.idea/
*.swp
*~

*.zip
*.DS_Store